---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Settori che Serviamo | Soluzioni Digitali per Ogni Business | Bitora"
  description="Soluzioni digitali su misura per ristoranti, turismo, professionisti e PMI in Piemonte. Scopri come possiamo aiutare il tuo settore a crescere online."
>
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white overflow-x-hidden selection:bg-gray-200 dark:selection:bg-white/20 selection:text-gray-900 dark:selection:text-white">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-white to-gray-50 dark:from-black dark:via-black dark:to-black/95"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 -right-20 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/10 blur-[100px] opacity-50"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase mb-4">I nostri settori</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
          Settori che<br />
          <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white">serviamo.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Ogni settore ha le sue sfide. Noi le conosciamo e abbiamo le soluzioni giuste. Scopri come possiamo aiutare la tua attività a crescere nel digitale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Sector Cards -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <a href="/settori/ristoranti" class="group p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-gray-400 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[340px] reveal-on-scroll">
            <div>
              <span class="text-4xl mb-4 block">🍕</span>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-gray-600 dark:group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Ristoranti e Locali</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Menu digitali, ordini WhatsApp, tessere NFC per recensioni Google e SEO locale. Tutto per far crescere il tuo locale nell'era digitale.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Scopri le soluzioni <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="/settori/turismo" class="group p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-gray-400 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[340px] reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
            <div>
              <span class="text-4xl mb-4 block">🏨</span>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-gray-600 dark:group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Turismo e Ospitalità</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Siti multilingua, booking diretto, SEO locale e Google Maps. Riduci la dipendenza dalle OTA e aumenta le prenotazioni dirette.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Scopri le soluzioni <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="/settori/professionisti" class="group p-8 md:p-10 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.03] border-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 hover:border-gray-400 dark:hover:border-white/30 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[340px] reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
            <div>
              <span class="text-4xl mb-4 block">⚖️</span>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-gray-600 dark:group-hover:text-gray-300 transition-colors">Professionisti</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Siti web autorevoli, CRM, portfolio e SEO locale per avvocati, commercialisti, consulenti e studi professionali.
              </p>
            </div>
            <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
              Scopri le soluzioni <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </span>
          </a>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Approccio -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-white/[0.02] border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Il nostro approccio</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Indipendentemente dal settore, il metodo è lo stesso: ascoltiamo, analizziamo, realizziamo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          {[
            { step: '01', title: 'Ascolto', desc: 'Capiamo il tuo settore, le tue sfide e i tuoi obiettivi specifici.' },
            { step: '02', title: 'Analisi', desc: 'Studiamo i competitor e identifichiamo le opportunità digitali.' },
            { step: '03', title: 'Sviluppo', desc: 'Realizziamo la soluzione su misura con le tecnologie più adatte.' },
            { step: '04', title: 'Crescita', desc: 'Monitoriamo i risultati e ottimizziamo continuamente.' }
          ].map((item, i) => (
            <div class="text-center reveal-on-scroll" style={`transition-delay: ${i * 100}ms`}>
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-200 dark:text-white/10">{item.step}</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-4 mb-3">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Non trovi il tuo settore? -->
    <section class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center reveal-on-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Non trovi il tuo settore?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8">
          Lavoriamo con aziende e professionisti di ogni tipo. Raccontaci la tua attività e troveremo la soluzione digitale giusta per te.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contattaci" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 min-w-[200px]">
            Richiedi consulenza gratuita
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/393514979670?text=Ciao%2C%20vorrei%20informazioni%20sulle%20vostre%20soluzioni.%20Ho%20visitato%20il%20sito%20bitora.it" class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 min-w-[200px]">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
            WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .reveal-on-scroll { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); }
  .reveal-on-scroll.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>

<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(entry => { if (entry.isIntersecting) { entry.target.classList.add('is-visible'); observer.unobserve(entry.target); } });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal-on-scroll').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  });
</script>
